name: ActRelationshipStartsAfterStartOf
title: ActRelationshipStartsAfterStartOf
description: The source Act starts after the start of the target Act (i.e. if we say "ActOne SAS ActTwo", it means that ActOne starts after the start of ActTwo, therefore ActOne is the source and ActTwo is the target).
